official_title: A bill to direct the Secretary of Agriculture to release a condition with respect to certain real property conveyed by the United States to the board of regents of the universities and State colleges of Arizona for the use of the University of Arizona.

summary.text: (Reported to House from the Committee on Interior and Insular Affaris with amendments, H. Rept. 94-1542) Directs the Secretary of Agriculture to enter into agreements as prescribed in this Act to release the board of regents of the universities and State colleges of Arizona from the requirement that specified lands transferred by the United States for the use of the University of Arizona be used only for research or educational purposes.
